### Metric
A metric is the latest validated reading from a sensor in your cluster.
Each metric has a signal_strength (0.0–1.0) reflecting the spatial
confidence of that sensor's contribution to this cell's reading.
Signal strength is determined by sensor distance — a wind sensor
further from its peers contributes a degraded signal compared to
closer sensors.
